The Claude Sound Notification extension does not collect, store, or transmit any user data whatsoever.

What we DON'T do:
- We do not collect personal information
- We do not track your browsing activity
- We do not store any data locally or remotely
- We do not use analytics or tracking services
- We do not share any information with third parties

What the extension DOES:
- Monitors claude.ai pages locally to detect when responses complete
- Plays a notification sound stored within the extension
- Saves your volume and enable/disable preferences locally in your browser

All functionality operates entirely within your browser. No external servers are contacted, and no data ever leaves your device.

Permissions used:
- "storage" - Only to save your volume and enable/disable preferences locally
- "tabs" - Only to detect if you're on claude.ai

If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please create an issue on our GitHub repository at https://github.com/luisdavidtrejosrojas/Claude-Sound-Notification
